===Adjective===
'''any'''

# A guaranteed [[selection]] from (a [[set]]). At [[least]] one, [[sometimes]] more (of a set).
#: ''Choose '''any''' items you want.''
#: '''''Any''' person may apply.''
#: (With negative:) ''I haven't got '''any''' money.''

